## 👋 About Me

I specialize in turning slow, manual processes into **intelligent, automated ecosystems**. My focus is on delivering measurable results: fewer hours wasted on repetitive tasks, fewer errors, more control.

I combine **Python**, **N8N**, and **REST API** integrations to build robust end-to-end automations — with an extra layer of attention to **information security** (currently pursuing a Cybersecurity degree, Cisco certified).

