## 🚀 Featured Projects

### 🤖 [Ryas](https://github.com/Kanashinho/RyasProject) — Proactive Local AI Assistant
> Desktop AI assistant running 100% offline — no cloud, no tracking, no limits.

- Multi-LLM integration via **Ollama + Llama3** with intent routing
- Fluid GUI with **PySide6 + QThreads** — zero interface freezing
- **Proactive Cybersecurity module**: "Byakugan" network scanner for real-time intruder detection
- Voice synthesis (**Coqui TTS**) and speech recognition (**Faster-Whisper**)

`Python` `PySide6` `Ollama` `Llama3` `Coqui TTS` `Faster-Whisper` `QThreads`

---

### 📦 [WyncStock](https://github.com/Kanashinho/SynckStock) — WhatsApp Inventory Management
> Inventory control system accessible via chat, eliminating manual entry errors.

- Real-time stock management directly through **WhatsApp**
- Integration between **N8N**, **Airtable**, and **Z-API**
- Eliminated 100% of manual typing errors in inventory control

`N8N` `Airtable` `Z-API` `WhatsApp API` `Low-Code`

---

### ⚙️ Humanized Quote Automation
> Multichannel automation that personalizes quote messages per customer profile using AI.

- Messages tailored by **LLM** for each customer profile
- Stack orchestrated via **Docker**: N8N + PostgreSQL + Evolution API
- Automated **WhatsApp** delivery with humanized language at scale

`N8N` `Docker` `PostgreSQL` `Evolution API` `Ollama` `WhatsApp API`

